### Register User
POST {{SafeVaultApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "AdminUser",
  "email": "admin.user@example.com",
  "password": "Password@123",
  "confirmPassword": "Password@123",
  "role": "Admin"
}

### Log in 
POST {{SafeVaultApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"adminUser",
    "password":"Password@123"
}

### Admin Only route
GET {{SafeVaultApi_HostAddress}}/api/users/admin
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}